<section id="science" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Proven by Science</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Medications mask symptoms. Our method addresses the root causes of cardiovascular disease using evidence-based nutrition and lifestyle interventions.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Our protocols are based on peer-reviewed research from institutions like Stanford, Harvard, and Johns Hopkins. We translate complex science into simple daily habits.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="flex -space-x-2">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">MD</div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">RD</div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">PhD</div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Trusted by 200+ healthcare providers</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Loved by our members</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">73%</div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">of members reduced their blood pressure within 90 days</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">67%</div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">improved their cholesterol panels without increasing medication</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">89%</div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">reported increased energy and better sleep quality</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-2">94%</div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">would recommend the program to family and friends</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
